name: Attack
note:

the Attack command.
<setup action>
display action
immortal: targets, true

<target action>
if user.attackMotion() !== 'missile'
move user: targets, front, 20
camera screen: target, front center, 20

zoom: 120%, 20
else
perform start
end
wait for movement
motion attack: user
wait: 10
attack animation: target
wait for animation
action effect

move user: home, 20
end
</target action>
